Is this your first PCB rodeo? (if yes, don't feel bad. you're all good): This is my first PCB rodeo.

What you are making?: I am making a remote control robot that uses Radio Waves/Bluetooth to search for people with an item. 

Inspiration: The inspiration for this project is a remote-controlled search drone capable of live streaming from the drone to a phone using radio waves.

